text: Río Iglesias is a corregimiento in Chepigana District, Darién Province, Panama with a population of 1,672 as of 2010. Its population as of 1990 was 1,348; its population as of 2000 was 1,468. ==See also== *Filo del Tallo ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Darién Province
title: Río Iglesias
